OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPersistent
OL,6,Frain through the evening, locally
OL,7,Fheavy in places, but clearing east by
OL,8,Fthe early hours. Mostly dry to follow
OL,9,Fwith occasional clear spells, although
OL,10,Fa few showers likely across western
OL,11,Fhills.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FSunny spells and isolated
OL,14,Fshowers, these most likely across
OL,15,Fwestern areas, until late afternoon.
OL,16,FThen frequent showers will spread
OL,17,Feast, locally heavy with a small
OL,18,Fchance of hail and thunder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
