OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMonday
OL,6,Fsunshine and scattered showers,
OL,7,Foccasionally heavy. Rain and strong
OL,8,Fwinds overnight. Tuesday breezy with
OL,9,Ffrequent heavy showers. Wednesday
OL,10,Fbreezy, bright spells and isolated
OL,11,Fshowers. Temperatures normal or
OL,12,Fslightly above.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
